.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: blue, green, red, white, yellow
Transport: train, skateboard, bus, snowmobile, helicopter
Sport: tennis, rugby, rowing, sailing, ice-hockey
Cigar: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
Pet: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. Transport:train == Color:red
2. Transport:swedish == Pet:dog
3. Transport:skateboard == Sport:sailing
4. Color:green is on the left of Color:white
5. Color:green == Sport:rugby
6. Cigar:pall-mall == Pet:bird
7. Color:yellow == Cigar:dunhill
8. Sport:rowing is in the middle
9. Transport:snowmobile is on the far left
10. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Pet:cat
11. Pet:horses is on the left or right of Cigar:dunhill
12. Cigar:bluemaster == Sport:tennis
13. Transport:bus == Cigar:prince
14. Transport:snowmobile is on the left or right of Color:blue
15. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Sport:ice-hockey

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Transport	|   snowmobile	|    skateboard	|    train	|    bus	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     cat	|    horse	|     bird	|     fish	|      dog	|
| Sport	|    ice-hockey	|     sailing	|     rowing	|    rugby	|      tennis	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   bluemaster	|
